  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0dc4\u0dcf \u0db0\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db7\u0dd6\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Kerosene from India for farmers and fishermen",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Arrangements have been made to import kerosene from India to Sri Lanka, Fisheries Minister Douglas Devananda said.",
        "Speaking further the Minister said that the non-availability of kerosene has become an obstacle for farmers and fishermen in Sri Lanka to pursue their economic activities and jobs. He said that in order to solve this problem, there is an opportunity to import 1500 kerosene containing 210 liters at a time from India.",
        "He also said that he had a telephone conversation with Ports and Shipping Minister Nimal Siripala de Silva and the Defense Secretary regarding the transportation of kerosene by ship and that he had received a favorable response and was confident that the process would be successful."
      ],
